Package net.cloud.client.nio.bufferable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Bufferable
    This is the interface that objects should implement when they are to be serializable.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BufferableInteger
    A wrapper around a primitive integer, that implements Bufferable.
    BufferableString
    A String wrapper that implements Bufferable, useful for when a Bufferable object is expected but the calling code has a String to provide.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BufferableException
    An exception for Bufferable methods to throw.
